11#include "sdk/objc/native/src/objc_video_frame.h"
12
13#include "rtc_base/time_utils.h"
14#include "sdk/objc/native/src/objc_frame_buffer.h"
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18RTCVideoFrame *ToObjCVideoFrame(const VideoFrame &frame) {
19 RTCVideoFrame *videoFrame =
20 [[RTCVideoFrame alloc] initWithBuffer:ToObjCVideoFrameBuffer(frame.video_frame_buffer())
21 rotation:RTCVideoRotation(frame.rotation())
22 timeStampNs:frame.timestamp_us() * rtc::kNumNanosecsPerMicrosec];
23 videoFrame.timeStamp = frame.timestamp();
24
25 return videoFrame;
26}
27
28} // namespace webrtc
